    <title>webcrawler-Wallhaven</title>
    <url>/2020/12/01/webcrawler-Wallhaven/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h1><p> <strong>网络爬虫</strong>（又称为网页蜘蛛，网络机器人，在FOAF社区中间，更经常的称为网页追逐者），是一种按照一定的规则，<strong>自动</strong>地抓取万维网信息的程序或者脚本。</p>
<h1 id="项目"><a href="#项目" class="headerlink" title="项目"></a>项目</h1><h2 id="项目目的"><a href="#项目目的" class="headerlink" title="项目目的"></a>项目目的</h2><p> 爬取<em>Wallhaven</em>上热门图片。</p>
<h2 id="实现方法"><a href="#实现方法" class="headerlink" title="实现方法"></a>实现方法</h2><p> 利用python的<strong>urlopen</strong>方法获取页面信息，进而读取图片的详情链接，进行访问；获取图片的下载链接，访问后对返回的内容进行解码，保存。</p>
<h2 id="具体代码"><a href="#具体代码" class="headerlink" title="具体代码"></a>具体代码</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import urllib.request</span><br><span class="line">import re</span><br><span class="line">import os</span><br><span class="line">from random import choice</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 链接访问</span><br><span class="line">def url_open(url):</span><br><span class="line">    list_headers &#x3D; [&#123;&#39;user-agent&#39;:&#39;Mozilla&#x2F;5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit&#x2F;537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome&#x2F;86.0.4240.198 Safari&#x2F;537.36&#39;,</span><br><span class="line">                    &#39;Referer&#39;:&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;wallhaven.cc&#x2F;&#39;&#125;,&#123;&#39;user-agent&#39;:&#39;Mozilla&#x2F;5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit&#x2F;537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome&#x2F;86.0.4240.190 Safari&#x2F;537.36&#39;,</span><br><span class="line">                    &#39;Referer&#39;:&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;wallhaven.cc&#x2F;&#39;&#125;,&#123;&#39;user-agent&#39;:&#39;Mozilla&#x2F;5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit&#x2F;537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome&#x2F;86.0.4240.192 Safari&#x2F;537.36&#39;,</span><br><span class="line">                    &#39;Referer&#39;:&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;wallhaven.cc&#x2F;&#39;&#125;,&#123;&#39;user-agent&#39;:&#39;Mozilla&#x2F;5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit&#x2F;537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome&#x2F;86.0.4240.194 Safari&#x2F;537.32&#39;,</span><br><span class="line">                    &#39;Referer&#39;:&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;wallhaven.cc&#x2F;&#39;&#125;]</span><br><span class="line">    try:</span><br><span class="line">        req &#x3D; urllib.request.Request(url,headers&#x3D;choice(list_headers))</span><br><span class="line">        respond &#x3D; urllib.request.urlopen(req)</span><br><span class="line">    except:</span><br><span class="line">        print(&#39;获取失败！&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">        num &#x3D; 0</span><br><span class="line">        print(num)</span><br><span class="line">    else:</span><br><span class="line">        num &#x3D; 1</span><br><span class="line">        print(num)</span><br><span class="line">        return respond</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 图片详情获取</span><br><span class="line">def dataillink_img(respond):</span><br><span class="line">    html &#x3D; respond.read().decode(&#39;utf-8&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">    p &#x3D; r&#39;a class&#x3D;&quot;preview&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;[^&quot;]+&quot;&#39;</span><br><span class="line">    list_detaillink &#x3D; re.findall(p,html)</span><br><span class="line">    list_detaillink2 &#x3D; []</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    for i in list_detaillink:</span><br><span class="line">        a &#x3D; 24</span><br><span class="line">        b &#x3D; i.find(&#39;&quot;&#39;,a)</span><br><span class="line">        list_detaillink2.append(i[a:b])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    for i in list_detaillink2:</span><br><span class="line">        print(i)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    print(&#39;捕获结束，得到%d个图片详情链接&#39;%len(list_detaillink2))</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    return list_detaillink2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#图片下载链接获取</span><br><span class="line">def downloadlink_img(list_detaillink2):</span><br><span class="line">    num &#x3D; 1</span><br><span class="line">    list_downloadlink2 &#x3D; []</span><br><span class="line">    for i in list_detaillink2:</span><br><span class="line">        respond &#x3D; url_open(i)</span><br><span class="line">        if(num !&#x3D; 0):</span><br><span class="line">            html &#x3D; respond.read().decode(&#39;utf-8&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">            p &#x3D; r&#39;img id&#x3D;&quot;wallpaper&quot; src&#x3D;&quot;([^&quot;]+g)&quot;&#39;</span><br><span class="line">            downloadlink &#x3D; re.search(p,html)</span><br><span class="line">            downloadlink2 &#x3D; downloadlink.group(1)</span><br><span class="line">            print(downloadlink2)</span><br><span class="line">            list_downloadlink2.append(downloadlink2)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    print(&#39;捕获结束，得到%d个图片下载链接&#39;%len(list_downloadlink2))</span><br><span class="line">    print(&#39;\n&#39;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    return list_downloadlink2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 图片下载</span><br><span class="line">def save_img(list_downloadlink2):</span><br><span class="line">    os.mkdir(&#39;gg&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">    os.chdir(&#39;gg&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">    num &#x3D; 1</span><br><span class="line">    many &#x3D; 0</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    for i in list_downloadlink2:</span><br><span class="line">        respond &#x3D; url_open(i)</span><br><span class="line">        if(num !&#x3D; 0):</span><br><span class="line">            respond &#x3D; respond.read()</span><br><span class="line">            filename &#x3D; i.split(&#39;&#x2F;&#39;)[5]</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">            with open (filename,&#39;wb&#39;) as f:</span><br><span class="line">                f.write(respond)</span><br><span class="line">                </span><br><span class="line">            many +&#x3D; 1</span><br><span class="line">            print(&#39;成功保存%s&#39; %filename)</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">    print(&#39;共保存%d张图片&#39;%many)</span><br><span class="line">    print(&#39;完成！&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 执行流程</span><br><span class="line">aurl &#x3D; &#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;wallhaven.cc&#x2F;hot?page&#x3D;5&#39;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(&#39;访问链接为：&#39;+aurl)</span><br><span class="line">print(&#39;正在获取图片的详情访问链接......&#39;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">arespond &#x3D; url_open(aurl)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">alist_detaillink2 &#x3D; dataillink_img(arespond)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(&#39;正在获取图片的下载链接......&#39;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">alist_downloadlink2 &#x3D; downloadlink_img(alist_detaillink2)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(&#39;正在保存图片......&#39;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">save_img(alist_downloadlink2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


